Great for parties and indoor、outdoor activities.

🚗【Best Gift For Toddler】- Suitable for toddlers playing at home indoor or outdoor activity, great Montessori toy gift for 1 2 3 4 5 6 years old boy and girl's birthday. 4 mini-cars are enough for 4 or more kids to play together at the party.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great toy when space is an issue
reviews.reviewText: This was purchased for my grandsons birthday and I was surprised at how small it was but it is very well made and my grandson, who turned two, loves it. The cars are a bit small so if you have a toddler that likes to put things in their mouths, you may want to think twice. It has held up well and is used often. Keeps him entertained for hours. The small size does make it great to store or for travel.
